Dominique CATHOLIC, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-2440 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. July 25, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition, docketed June 21, 2018, is transferred to case 2D17-5117 as an amended petition. Case 2D18-2440 is dismissed as a duplicate to case 2D17-5117.

MORRIS, SLEET, and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
